 Despite a looming threat by big Nigerian banks in the space, Nigeria’s self-styled ‘Bank of the free’, Kuda Bank may be a serious contender to the digital banking throne in the country. Kuda Bank has secured $10 million seed round led by Target Global, Berlin-based venture capital, and participation from Entrée Capital and SBI Investment…. Projected US President-elect Joe Biden on Tuesday appointed Gary Gensler, a Washington and Wall Street financial expert who has closely monitored the evolution of the cryptocurrency market, to lead his financial policy transition team. This is coming at a time when the volume of bitcoin transactions has been on an impressive bullish run, surging more…